The paper deals with knowledge representation and completion using machine learning techniques, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) and Self-Organised Maps (SOM). This falls under the domain of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of CNNs also suggests a possible connection to Computer Vision (cs.CV). The paper also deals with data management and retrieval, which could fall under Databases (cs.DB) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the application of these techniques to biomedical data suggests a possible connection to Bioinformatics (q-bio.QM). However, since the paper is published on arXiv CS, we will limit our answer to CS sub-categories.
